                                        Some of the threats under NIS investigation, e.g. terrorism, can have criminal implications. 
                                        In such cases, the Kenya Police Criminal Investigation Department (CID) would investigate and lay the appropriate criminal charges.                                      
                                    </strong> 
                                    </div>
                                </div>
